Mike Reid (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mike_Reid_(actor) 0 Michael Reid (19 January 1940 – 29 July 2007) was an English comedian, actor, author and occasional television presenter from London, who is best remembered for playing the role of Frank Butcher in EastEnders and hosting the popular children's TV show Runaround. He was noted for his gravelly voice and strong Cockney accent.
